This is the first record of 
<taxonomicName box="[613,732,1908,1932]" class="Arachnida" family="Eriophyidae" genus="Aceria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Prostigmata" pageId="7" pageNumber="356" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cichorii">
